properties.headline: Winter Weather Advisory issued February 1 at 5:52AM AKST until February 2 at 3:00AM AKST by NWS Juneau AK
properties.description:
* WHAT...Snow. Additional snow accumulations of 3 to 8 inches.

* WHERE...Juneau.

* WHEN...Until 3 AM AKST Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Travel could be very difficult. Visibility will be
very poor in heavier snow showers.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Amounts will be highly variable with
heaviest showers most likely this afternoon and this evening.
There will be periods of little or no snowfall followed by
moderate to heavy snow squalls.
properties.instruction:
Slow down and use caution while traveling.

For the latest road conditions call 5 1 1 or visit
511.alaska.gov.

NWSheadline: WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 3 AM AKST SUNDAY
